![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0f746c41-b2a3-40b3-967f-5af7fb9f1141/237.jpg)

Superman and Lois was a delightful show in its first season, laying the groundwork for future conflicts and adventures in the world of Smallville. Season 2 has just wrapped up but was it able to do the same? Join us as we talk about Superman and Lois Season 2, Bizzaro, Parasite and all things The Kents in this incredibly fun recap and review of one of the best shows currently on TV!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

  
